    headband_common, circlet_common, sword_common\n3. Drag them into the ItemDatabase
    component's 'Item Definitions' array\n4. Use the test methods below to validate
    setup\n5. This component should be on the same GameObject as ItemDatabase"
  database: {fileID: 8878757998277660580}
